Output docs/demo.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 650
Set Padding 20
Set Shell zsh

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/demo-fresh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "agents-sync init ."
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 38s

Type "ls"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 1000ms

Type "head -30 AGENTS.md"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
